Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Misleading headlines
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xdch
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Jun 1984
Misleading headlines skew findings of support for the President's policies in Central America. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less